Install the external libraries required:
                                                                                                                                        
- TAUCS (Version >= 2.0)
- METIS
- LAPACK and BLAS (Fortran)
- GSL (Version >= 1.8)
- ZLib

You may also want to replace BLAS and LAPACK (partly) with the more
optimised versions in
 
- ATLAS
 
If these are not already installed, the source-code for the required
libraries is available in the EXTLIBS directory.

edit Makefile, then type

	make

and then

	make install
